=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=127c4c96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F20770339&h=b658236b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190918/20770339</a><br />\n<br />\n穗維權者上載《榮光》被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190918/large/1568738378_182c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190918%2Flarge%2F1568738378_182c.gif&h=6d819c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賴日福今年4月穿公民抗命T恤聲援香港「佔中九子」。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】曾因參與抗爭行動而被多次拘留的廣州維權人士賴日福，日前被當地公安以涉嫌「尋釁滋事」在家中被捕。據悉他曾在微信及fb上載短片，影片配樂是被官方標籤為「港獨歌」的《願榮光歸香港》，疑因此出事。賴日福是南方街頭運動成員，因參與抗爭維權，曾先後兩次被當局刑拘。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「消失三人」均為重傷者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾穿T恤聲援佔中九子<br />\n<br />\n南方街頭運動fb專頁前晚深夜發文指，賴日福（網名「花滿樓」）周日晚與7歲兒子回到廣州家中時被捕，孩子目睹父親被不明男子撲倒在地帶走，受驚過度整夜啼哭。家屬前晚收到公安的刑拘通知書，指賴涉「尋釁滋事」，目前被關在廣州市越秀區拘留所。<br />\n<br />\n據透露，賴上周五曾在微信及fb上載一段影片，配樂是《願榮光歸香港》，拍攝的是他家鄉的風景，並配文「這是我的祖國，我要讓她自由！」當局近日大舉掃蕩網絡言論，特別是針對涉港發言，賴疑因此被盯上。他今年4月曾因穿公民抗命T恤，聲援香港被判刑的「佔中九子」被拘留。南方街頭運動三名成員謝文飛、王默、張聖雨，曾因聲援港雨傘運動，被控「煽顛罪」，判監4年至4年半，今年陸續出獄。<br />\n<br />\n■記者沈燕媚 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n港生聯合國演說：不做疆藏<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n台︰少於60港人求助<br />\n<br />\n「消失三人」均為重傷者<br />\n三職員挺身爆料 轟警阻救援<br />\n新同盟報廉署控警行為失當<br />\n西環集中營：京反對法案 證明有殺傷力<br />\n泛民設小組 游說國際制裁林鄭<br />\n民建聯見美領事 稱北京或反擊<br />\n港生聯合國演說：不做疆藏<br />\n台︰少於60港人求助<br />\n彭定康：京須表明遵守聯合聲明<br />\n岳男控襲警 庭外人海力挺<br />\n「香港人加油」護送囚車離去<br />\n許智峯獲釋 民事起訴警濫捕<br />\n港台司機6.12中彈 向盧偉聰索償<br />\n16歲仔夜收工 官不准延宵禁時間<br />\n七成受訪差人：警執法不公<br />\n大律師公會兩函盧偉聰斥警阻見被捕者<br />\n監警會變關警會 600人要輔導<br />\n黃絲警：前線已情緒失控<br />\n「飛天南」7.21涉暴動被捕<br />\n倘300人踩場 今夜馬取消<br />\n2,000網民曾聯署促退役<br />\n400人中環拖手聲援新屋嶺被捕者<br />\n敵對球迷今維園聚首大合唱<br />\n民意唾棄行會 湯家驊墊底<br />\n防白衣人 張祝珊校籲結伴放學<br />\n憂受欺凌 興德三跨境學童退學<br />\n林鄭撐警暴 下周搞對話騷<br />\n沈旭暉邀百學者晤青年<br />\n穆迪降港鐵評級展望至負面<br />\n國泰前空姐：炒我嗰日20人被裁<br />\n陳啟宗：地產商自私 非亂局根源<br />\n消防改17紀錄 36分鐘空白"},{"pid":"558652c386f7657184ce7923c03f809be4051909","tid":1577523,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T00:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227cfc889f7c64ca22d0926c8881177b6ca844fa","tid":1577523,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T00:28:20.000Z","msg":"勇者"},{"pid":"59987fff9734ba1341d8293f2ad72ea2cb42327a","tid":1577523,"uid":10984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T00:31:49.000Z","msg":"真大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440cd0217735671ed270b64ddd87ecc329e96c99","tid":1577523,"uid":246741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T00:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好勇武"},{"pid":"68a9d7b71ae5be7f8b937173f700b025f757c72f","tid":1577523,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T00:34:54.000Z","msg":"反攻大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國軍來了 我加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ff47266fd7c0e50c17254972ef2c9955a8ea42","tid":1577523,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T00:36:12.000Z","msg":"新冷戰之中嘅西柏林，亡共必港嘅反共前線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566716</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[長文，本地&amp;國際文宣，集結全世界反共] 點解我地要有反共嘅心態？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563828</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1d6580b802211a1df3368f758035b419c1ff52bf","tid":1577523,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T00:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd129a082f7666bc5d2450038c68f7782fea7fd","tid":1577523,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T00:56:30.000Z","msg":"烈士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4fa055848e8de587c2c8fa5a9901ce58bf515a","tid":1577523,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:23:18.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"793a94e1e8fa573c30f80a65bcda43d3e50e00e4","tid":1577523,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:40:55.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y&amp;list=FLn1jpxUqDh0Iftde5CY0luw&amp;index=3&amp;t=0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7yRDOLCy4Y%26list%3DFLn1jpxUqDh0Iftde5CY0luw%26index%3D3%26t%3D0s&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=cbc63ab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y&amp;list=FLn1jpxUqDh0Iftde5CY0luw&amp;index=3&amp;t=0s</a><br />\n<br />\nA1<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\n<br />\nA2<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲響透<br />\n建自由 光輝香港<br />\n<br />\nB<br />\n在晚星 墜落徬徨午夜<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處吹來 號角聲<br />\n捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣智慧 也永不滅<br />\n<br />\nA3<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\n祈求民主 與自由 萬世都不朽<br />\n我願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"a37b055ef2414e8e615743d12e181e8a8a725733","tid":1577523,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:40:59.000Z","msg":"大陸upload呢啲真係好勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}